00276 void CalvinCHPMultiDataFileUpdaterTest::testMultiData1()
00277 {
00278         CreateReferenceFile1();
00279 
00280     vector<ColumnInfo> cols;
00281         CalvinCHPMultiDataFileUpdater upd;
00282     ProbeSetMultiDataGenotypeData e;
00283         upd.Initialize(TEST1_FILE);
00284 
00285     e.call = 11;
00286     e.confidence = 111.0f;
00287         upd.UpdateMultiData(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0, e);
00288 
00289     e.call = 22;
00290     e.confidence = 222.0f;
00291         upd.UpdateMultiData(GenotypeMultiDataType, 2, e);
00292 
00293         CHPMultiDataData data;
00294         CHPMultiDataFileReader reader;
00295         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(reader.SetFilename(TEST1_FILE));
00296         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(reader.Read(data));
00297         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.GetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 4);
00298 
00299     data.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0, e);
00300         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "1");
00301         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.call == 11);
00302     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.confidence, 111.0f, 0.000001f);
00303         data.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 1, e);
00304         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "2");
00305         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.call == 2);
00306         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.confidence, 20.0f, 0.000001f);
00307         data.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 2, e);
00308         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "3");
00309         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.call == 22);
00310         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.confidence, 222.0f, 0.000001f);
00311         data.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 3, e);
00312         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "4");
00313         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.call == 4);
00314         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.confidence, 40.0f, 0.000001f);
00315 }
